%F A057087 Limit_{n->oo} A084128(n)/A057087(n-1) = sqrt(2). (End)
%F A057087 a(n) = 4^n*hypergeom([1/2-n/2, -n/2], [-n], -1) for n>=1. - _Peter Luschny_, Dec 17 2015
